data.description: MOUNTAIN VIEW!!!! Come check out this great starter home or if your planning on downsizing, you will enjoy the privacy and mountain views this property offers. 3 carports and a storage building that will remain with property. Property has a permanent brick foundation. Covered deck in back, small open deck in front. Tile countertops also tile in living room and Master bedroom.
